Class InspectorToolImpl

  • java.lang.Object

    InspectorTool

    public class InspectorToolImpl
extends AbstractKbTool
implements InspectorTool
    Tools for examining individual CycObjects. To examine the relationship between different CycObjects, use the ComparisonToolImpl.

    nwinant
